WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:41.720 --> 00:00:44.180
-Who are you?
-We are three wise men.

00:00:44.350 --> 00:00:46.930
-What?
-We are three wise men.

00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:50.140
What are you doing creeping around
a cowshed at 2:00 a.m.?

00:00:50.310 --> 00:00:52.270
That doesn't sound very wise to me.

00:00:52.820 --> 00:00:56.650
-We are astrologers.
-We have come from the East.

00:00:57.030 --> 00:01:01.200
-ls this some kind of joke?
-We wish to praise the infant.

00:01:01.370 --> 00:01:04.950
-We must pay a homage to him.
-Homage? You're all drunk!

00:01:05.120 --> 00:01:07.540
lt's disgusting! Out! Come on, out!

00:01:07.700 --> 00:01:11.290
Bursting in here with tales about
Oriental fortunetellers. Out!

00:01:11.500 --> 00:01:14.380
-No, no, we must see him.
-Go and praise someone else's brat!

00:01:14.550 --> 00:01:18.510
-We were led by a star!
-Led by a bottle more like! Go on, out!

00:01:18.670 --> 00:01:21.050
-We must see him. We have presents!
-Out!

00:01:21.220 --> 00:01:23.140
Gold, frankincense, myrrh!

00:01:23.300 --> 00:01:26.350
Well, why didn't you say?
He's over there.

00:01:26.520 --> 00:01:29.730
Sorry the place is a bit of a mess.

00:01:29.890 --> 00:01:31.890
Well, what is myrrh anyway?

00:01:32.060 --> 00:01:34.730
-lt is a valuable balm.
-A balm?!

00:01:34.900 --> 00:01:37.650
What are you giving him a balm for?
lt might bite him!

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:40.070
-What?
-That's a dangerous animal!

00:01:40.240 --> 00:01:41.950
-Throw it in the trough!
-No, it isn't!

00:01:42.110 --> 00:01:46.080
-lt's a great big...
-No, no, no, it is an ointment.

00:01:46.580 --> 00:01:50.370
Well, there is an animal called
a balm, or did l dream it?

00:01:50.540 --> 00:01:54.380
So you're astrologers, are you?
Well, what is he then?

00:01:54.540 --> 00:01:57.590
What star-sign is he?

00:01:57.750 --> 00:02:01.380
-Capricorn.
-Capricorn, eh? What are they like?

00:02:01.550 --> 00:02:04.220
Well, he's the Son of God.
Our Messiah.

00:02:04.430 --> 00:02:05.550
King of the Jews!

00:02:05.720 --> 00:02:09.020
-And that's Capricorn, is it?
-No, no, no, that's just him!

00:02:09.180 --> 00:02:12.440
I was gonna say,
otherwise there'd be a lot of them.

00:02:12.600 --> 00:02:16.060
-By what name are you calling him?
-Brian.

00:02:16.230 --> 00:02:20.480
We worship you, Brian,
who are lord over us all.

00:02:20.860 --> 00:02:26.030
Praise unto you, Brian,
and to the Lord, our Father. Amen.

00:02:26.200 --> 00:02:27.700
-Do you do a lot of this?
-What?

00:02:27.870 --> 00:02:29.950
-This praising.
-No, no. No, no.

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:32.960
Well, if you're dropping
by again, do pop in.

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:35.880
And thanks a lot for the gold
and frankincense...

00:02:36.040 --> 00:02:39.210
...but don't worry too much about
the myrrh next time, all right?

00:02:39.380 --> 00:02:42.630
Thank you. Goodbye.

00:02:43.880 --> 00:02:45.890
Well, weren't they nice?

00:02:46.050 --> 00:02:50.350
Out of their bloody minds'
but still, look at that!

00:02:50.640 --> 00:02:54.770
Here. here, that's mine! Hey! Hey!

00:03:09.450 --> 00:03:11.160
Shut up!

